# Site Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://campustoolshub.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=https://campustoolshub.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_NAME=CampusToolsHub
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_DESCRIPTION=Ultimate productivity hub for college students with 20+ free tools including GPA calculator, resume builder, study timer, and more
